to experience and walk away.

596
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:34,400
I know Wasem won't just walk away.

597
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:36,400
Which is why it's a good reason

598
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:39,700
for us all to lay low for a bit.

599
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:44,500
So, I was thinking,
when this job is done,

600
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:47,800
we should take a break.

601
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,000
Go our separate ways for a while.

602
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:52,900
- How long's a while?
- Who knows?

603
00:37:52,900 --> 00:37:54,900
I thought it best
not to make plans.

604
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:59,400
I was going to talk to you about
this when the job was done but...

605
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,700
