606
00:38:01,700 --> 00:38:04,700
So, that's why we're taking this
job? It's walking away money?

607
00:38:04,700 --> 00:38:07,300
- If you want to call it that.
- That's it, then?

608
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:10,700
One last job
and we're finished, huh?

609
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:14,700
I've always thought it was a good
idea to quit while you're ahead.

610
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:19,800
I think ten million
qualifies as being ahead.

611
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:22,300
This is the question.

612
00:38:22,300 --> 00:38:24,500
If you didn't take this break,

613
00:38:25,300 --> 00:38:27,600
