614
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,900
If I'm honest.

615
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:39,000
No, I wouldn't.

616
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:42,800
And I wouldn't blame any one of you
that wanted to walk away right now.

617
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:47,100
But, come on!
The money comes in tomorrow.

618
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:49,200
Our play is that the
City of London police

619
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:50,400
has had us under surveillance.

620
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:54,100
Ash has lined up a dozen
grifters and all the vehicles.

621
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:56,300
We get ourselves arrested
but we let Wasem get away.

622
00:38:56,300 --> 00:38:59,000
